{"type": "article", "id": 25067, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-07T07:10:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25917, "name": "Axis Design"}, {"id": 25918, "name": "People People"}, {"id": 25919, "name": "AUDIO DEVA"}, {"id": 25920, "name": "Studio Vørding"}, {"id": 25921, "name": "Rik ten Velden"}, {"id": 25922, "name": "Arihiro Miyake"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132616w13eTqnGi65Ct7af.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Selectors Cabinet by Studio Rik ten Velden</h2>\n<p>这是荷兰设计师 Rik ten Velden 新推出的储物柜，外形方正且简洁干净。抽屉本身并没有凹槽，只通过抽屉之间的横竖细长线条来区分不同的板块，方形的柜子外面外面增加了黑色金属框架，以强调了这种线条感。柜子本身带有可插入电线的缺口，可以用来连接键盘或者电脑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182034hw6q7ITkWQFER5bf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182034xPI7SBZzDmfQCkUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820357R6OIw1VQ3e0NHiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182035lroRnLh3UdCvDmQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182036MHf58Pq9mBygI40p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Coppélia by Arihiro Miyake &amp; Moooi</h2>\n<p>这是日本设计师 Arihiro Miyake 为丹麦品牌 Moooi 设计的吊灯，使用非常细的金属框架和 54 盏 LED 灯泡，搭建出 3 层环形灯，相互错落又显得很有规律，远看就像是三圈蜡烛。每一盏 LED 灯都有两根金属丝牵引指向中心的轴，分别是正负两极，这些线条穿插本身也形成了精细的感受。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182036lGEWOn0BeJ8MwzyH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820370elPm5SiJpuN6yrf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182037tnoOAFGSblZXDB7i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820381257Yq9iQRhPUjra.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182038kzac0nreoPALu6Zp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>LooLedge by Axis Design</h2>\n<p>不少人都有将手机掉进厕所里的经历，在卷纸架上增加一个放手机的平台是再正常不过的。这组卷纸架的设计来自美国设计公司 Axis Design，放卷纸的轴心上连着一个与地面平行的平台，只在平台外增加了一个很浅的挡板，整体设计简洁干净而没有多余的地方。<a href=\"http://www.axisdesign.com\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820395H0IYDQ76RpJgaNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182039BpziGrWVPnM1wUyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182040sgWCZKDPuVGeOlHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182041LH3qfkuVmeO4gMC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182041cD3j7omxYCBuevsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Axcent Pocket Watch by People People </h2>\n<p>这款怀表是给那些还习惯于看手表而不是手机的人，它带有明显的怀旧成分。金属表盘本身非常简洁，用长短线条刻痕来表刻度，只有时针和分针两个指示时间，并不十分精确或清晰，但能带给人更多的纪念意义。怀表直径 45 毫米，很小巧。有棕色和灰色两种，售价 165 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/mens-watches/axcent-pocket-watch/?v=79cba1185463\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182041lAHOJ4ectpIoEF92.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50854701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182042qHD2hI4oXdTZC6pi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820431nE3oGiNqOYSKgbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182043CwknlXzes2cd63pE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92094017\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182043YMJEgik9py2LU8tr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91346154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ATMO SFERA by AUDIO DEVA </h2>\n<p>这是一款非常轻巧的黑胶唱片播放器，来自意大利的设计团队 AUDIO DEVA。他们改进了原本播放器笨重的形象，将基座设计成三角形，更配合现代家居环境。而主体材料采用铝合金，减轻了播放器的重量。其中唱臂管壳的重量是 2 克，不会压坏唱片本身。产品目前在众筹，预计今年 9 月份上市，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/959799437/atmo-sferatm-platterless-turntable?ref=nav_search\">这里是众筹链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182044JutCSPV4bYkUsrQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182044nyK3ZW0U9r4JhdeE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182045WzscZ1tHACuBwjd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182045kACZcI4L6mosbFVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182046GsIv7ekDhXS26oyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Vørding’s Gin packaging by Studio Vørding</h2>\n<p>这瓶 Gin 装在可容纳 700 毫升的大玻璃瓶里，有着典雅的形状和亮度很高的金黄色。特别在于在酒瓶中放了一根很细的雪松木条强调酒本身的颜色和在木材中泡制的成分。雪松木是调制这款酒的配方之一，使这瓶酒拥有更细腻的口感。这瓶酒产于阿姆斯特丹，在设计上也追求简洁干净的体验，包括大的玻璃瓶和瓶身上的白色贴纸。<a href=\"http://www.vordingsgin.com\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182047GCVEfP8yxwKv0X5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182047dIYJQ8VWL6n7cDhF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071820482camkq8R3sAZpijX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182048mDuLBJ8ditOfkHbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607182048DmIWJOxKCRSlkoTN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}